40
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:47,900
were so useful.

41
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:49,300
Are you just teasing me?

42
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:50,980
Not at all.

43
00:01:52,180 --> 00:01:53,020
Oh.

44
00:01:58,140 --> 00:01:58,980
Jiang.

45
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,420
Why are you here?

46
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:22,860
I want to see you.

47
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:26,300
Didn't we agree,

48
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,140
we wouldn't meet again?

49
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:29,780
I don't agree to break up.

50
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,460
What do you want then?

51
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:48,820
Yao Yuan.

52
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:50,540
I miss you so much.

53
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,500
Don't break up with me.

54
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,620
