♪Forget me and start a new life♪

60
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:35,980
Jiang.

61
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:38,460
Give her some time.

62
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:43,300
In your current state,

63
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:45,380
I think you need to adjust.

64
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:47,620
Don't lose her

65
00:03:49,380 --> 00:03:50,300
and also the company.

66
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:56,140
Take care of her for me.

67
00:03:59,220 --> 00:04:00,060
I will.

68
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,620
Don't worry.

